  <title>Start a new game</title>

  <p>To start a new game, click <guiseq><gui>Game</gui><gui>New</gui>
    </guiseq>, then <link xref="difficulty">select your preferred difficulty 
    level</link>.
  </p>
  <p>If you were playing already a game, a popup message will ask if you want
  to <gui>Start new game</gui> or <gui>Keep current Game</gui>, if you choose 
  the former, your current game will be lost.
  </p>

